        "main_heading": "Two women on a mission",
        "sub_heading": "",
        "heading": "",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/c0855ba36e497bb2acf6ef7605222d4a.jpg",
        "details": "<span class=\"fw-400\">Best friends Purdy &amp; Charlotte were fed up with cupboards cluttered with toxic products.</span><span class=\"fw-300\"> Both firm believers in the power of natural cleaning, they experimented with formulas in an empty garage until they landed on an all natural, multipurpose spray, beautifully scented with essential oils. They called it Counter Clean. </span>",
        "man_details_1": "We manufacture Purdy &amp; Figg cleaning concentrates in England, where we’re subject to stringent health regulations.",
        "man_details_2": "Every Purdy &amp; Figg concentrate is made in a state-of-the-art laboratory. We promise we’ll never cut corners when it comes to your health or safety.",
        "btnLabel": "GET OFFER",
